      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZABDON JUSTICE (1) did a good job to finish second last time out over 350m at this track (19.09) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Will find this more suitable and can atone. HOOKED ON TORQUE (8) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fourth (19.87) at this track. Deserves plenty of respect. UNPAID DEBT (4) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 1.75 lengths from Key Change in third (19.76) at Q Lakeside. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in four starts. Expecting another good run. FEDERAL LOTUS (2) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.",
